Are you traveling to The Arab Emirates and need Emirati Dirham (AED)? At FOREX, you can easily buy AED for your trip. We offer both online purchases and personal service in our stores.

When you buy AED online, you can choose to have your currency delivered to the nearest postal agent or pick it up at any of our stores. Our goal is to make your Emirati Dirham order simple and hassle-free.

With the currency converter, you can calculate AED to SEK and stay fully informed about the current exchange rate. The currency graph shows the historical development of Emirati Dirham against your local currency over time. You can choose a timeframe from 2012 up to today.
